<section id="offer" class="py-24 lg:py-32" style="background:#0A0A0A;">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 reveal">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-accent/30 text-accent-light text-sm font-medium mb-6" style="background:rgba(79,70,229,0.1);">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-highlight rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        Vagas abertas esta semana
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">
        Agende seu Diagnóstico Gratuito
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
        Uma sessão de 30 minutos, sem compromisso, para entender o seu negócio e descobrir onde a IA pode gerar mais resultado para você.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 items-stretch reveal">

      <!-- What's included -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 h-full" style="background:rgba(17,24,39,0.8);">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-6">O que acontece no Diagnóstico</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(79,70,229,0.2);">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mapeamento de processos críticos</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">Conversamos sobre o contexto da sua empresa, os processos do dia a dia e os principais desafios operacionais.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(79,70,229,0.2);">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Identificação de oportunidades com IA</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">Mapeamos juntos onde a inteligência artificial pode gerar mais impacto e eficiência na sua operação.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(79,70,229,0.2);">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Estimativa de ROI por iniciativa</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">Cada oportunidade identificada vem com uma estimativa de economia e tempo de retorno do investimento.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(79,70,229,0.2);">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Próximos passos personalizados</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">Saindo da conversa, você já sabe exatamente o que faz sentido para o seu negócio e como avançar.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing card -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4F46E5,#7C3AED);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">
          <!-- Glow -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" style="background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(255,255,255,0.2),transparent 60%);"></div>

          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-2">Diagnóstico Gratuito</div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">Grátis</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-8">diagnóstico online · 30 minutos</div>

            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Entendimento do seu negócio
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Identificação de oportunidades com IA
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Próximos passos personalizados
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Sem compromisso
              </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Calendly embed or CTA -->
            <a href="<%= calendly.url %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               class="block w-full text-center py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold text-accent bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Marque um horário gratuito →
            </a>

            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
              <a href="https://wa.me/<%= whatsapp.number %>?text=<%= encodeURIComponent(whatsapp.message) %>"
                 target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                 class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                ou falar antes pelo WhatsApp
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
